data.description: Welcome Home! Right when you walk through the front door, you will see the open spacious floor plan. This home has 4 bedrooms & 2 bathrooms. Luxury Vinyl Flooring throughout the home. Custom faux wood blinds throughout the home from Just Blinds. Family room has cozy stone fireplace with a natural wood mantel & recessed lighting. Kitchen has all stainless-steel appliances and recessed lighting. Kitchen has large gray kitchen island with sink and white quartz countertop. Plenty of cabinets for storage that also has white quartz countertops. Kitchen has not one, but two pantries. Off the kitchen, you will find the spacious main bedroom. En-Suite bathroom with tile walk-in shower, garden tub, double vanities with quartz countertop, linen closet, separate toilet, and extra-large walk-in closet. Home is a spilt floor plan and the 3 guest bedrooms are on opposite side of home. All three bedrooms has large closets. Guest bathroom has Brookfield marble vinyl tile flooring, linen closet, and quartz countertop. Home has oversized laundry room with quartz countertop. Home has spray foam insultation and energy saving windows. Back covered patio with recess lighting and wood burning fireplace perfect for BBQ's and entertaining family and friends. Home has two car garage. Neighborhood has a small pond with plenty of brim and bass to fish. Pine Level School is .5 miles from home and Marbury High School is 3 miles. Home is eligible for 100% USDA financing.
